General Motors Corp. Chevrolet division dey react to slow sales, e say e go offer $800 monthly bill wey be sey na two door dey for en core compact car side.

Just three weeks na im dem dey sell give Beretta, plus en four door sister car, di Corsica sotay GM come idle di two plant wey dey build di motor for three weeks.

Di corsica and Beretta dey do di highest volume motor for Chevrolet, but dem sell di motor komot nine percent for di year, come fall 34% for October.

Chevrolet don already dey offer $800 bonus on di 1990 model, wey be Corsica.

Latest money wey dey come from inside Beretta model na im dey good.

Chevrolet buyers go fit take di money, or de go get discount rate wey go range from six9% on 24 months to 109% on 60 months loan.

